('trollstore', 'TrollInstallerDark', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22815c7874b8.46474010.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 10, '1.0', '5.8 MB', NULL, 'TrollInstallerDark is a modified version of TrollInstallerX by Alfie that uses the DarkSword kernel exploit to install TrollStore on supported iPhone and iPad devices.\n\nIt supports arm64 devices running iOS 15.7.2 to iOS 15.8.x and installs TrollStore directly to your Home Screen without needing a jailbreak. The app also sets up a persistence helper inside a system app you choose, helping TrollStore stay active after rebooting your device.\n\nYou can install the TrollInstallerDark IPA using sideloading tools like SideStore, KSign, iLoader, or PlumeImpactor. An open-source download is available on the GitHub TrollInstallerDark IPA Releases page.', 'https://github.com/rockylabs-dev/TrollInstallerDark/releases/download/1.0/TrollInstallerDark.ipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d75c0a0d7.10580190.jpg"]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollDecrypt', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22815d484661.20133150.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 20, '1.2.3', '3.3 MB', NULL, 'TrollDecryptJB is a powerful iOS app decryption tool designed for jailbroken devices. It allows you to decrypt and extract apps that require higher iOS versions — like iOS 18 or iOS 26 — while still running older firmware such as iOS 14–16.\n\nThis tool is based on the original TrollDecrypt app (for TrollStore users) but offers deeper system-level access using an LLDB-based decryption method developed by 82flex.\n\nTrollDecryptJB lets you decrypt iOS apps directly from your device by attaching to the app process before Apple’s FairPlay encryption loads. This unique timing allows the tool to dump the unencrypted app binary (Mach-O) and frameworks before protection is applied.', 'https://github.com/donato-fiore/TrollDecrypt/releases/download/v1.2.3/TrollDecrypt.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollInstallerX', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22815e190a16.28268909.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 30, '1.0', '6.6 MB', NULL, 'TrollInstallerX IPA – Easy TrollStore Installation for iOS 14 to iOS 17 Devices\n\nTrollInstallerX is a powerful tool that installs TrollStore on supported iPhones and iPads running iOS 14.0 to 17.0. It works on both arm64 and arm64e devices, using the best method for your specific iOS version and device type.\n\nKey Features:', 'https://github.com/alfiecg24/TrollInstallerX/releases/download/1.0.3/TrollInstallerX.ipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d7738bae6.12874221.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollFools', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22815f0d7f88.63654297.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 40, '4.3-246', '5.8 MB', NULL, 'TrollFools – Inject Tweaks into App Store Apps.\n\nThe TrollFools app lets you inject tweaks directly into App Store apps using insert_dylib and ChOma, which are all built with SwiftUI. It works in place, meaning no extra steps or complex setups!\n\n✅ Compatible with all iOS versions supported by TrollStore (by opa334).✅ Easily modify App Store apps with custom tweaks.', 'https://github.com/Lessica/TrollFools/releases/download/v4.3-246/TrollFools_4.3-246.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d784b2085.49657197.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'VansonMod', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22815fdc7100.49997530.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 50, '2.3', '', NULL, 'VansonMod is an advanced memory editing tool for iPhone and iPad, developed by vaenshine and available as an open-source project on GitHub. It allows users to scan, edit, and control live memory values inside running iOS apps.\n\nUnlike basic hex editors, VansonMod is designed specifically for iOS system behavior, including ASLR (Address Space Layout Randomization). This makes it especially useful for reverse engineers, researchers, and advanced users who need precise control over app memory.\n\nVansonMod runs directly on the device and does not require a constant PC connection, making it ideal for on-the-go testing and analysis.', 'https://github.com/vaenshine/VansonMod/releases/download/v2.3/VansonMod_v2.3.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'iOS Clean Pro', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228160ae67c3.45264115.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 60, '1.3', '', NULL, 'iOS Clean Pro is a powerful storage cleaner for TrollStore-supported iPhones. It removes hidden junk files, caches, and system leftovers with one tap—freeing up gigabytes of space instantly. Unlike normal cleaners, it performs deep system-level cleaning safely and includes a Clean Whitelist to protect your data.\n\niOS Clean Pro is a storage optimization app built for TrollStore users who want full control over iPhone cleanup. It doesn’t require jailbreaking and runs entirely offline.\n\nThe app scans for temporary files, app leftovers, OTA remnants, and Safari caches — helping you recover hidden storage space while keeping your device secure.', 'https://files.onejailbreak.com/iOSCleanPro1.3.ipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollVNC', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a2281617c48b4.39722229.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 70, '2.0', '', NULL, 'TrollVNC for iOS – Remote Access Made Simple\n\nTrollVNC is a powerful VNC server for iOS that allows you to remotely view and control your iPhone or iPad screen from another device. It supports iOS 16 up to iOS 17.0 and works smoothly on devices compatible with TrollStore.\n\nOriginally launched as a free, open-source hobby project, TrollVNC gave users full access to its source code. You could download, modify, and even compile it yourself. With version 2.0 and later, TrollVNC shifted to a paid model on Havoc ($6.99), offering pre-built binaries, updates, and dedicated support. However, the last free release (v1.6) is still available for those who prefer the open-source experience.', 'https://files.onejailbreak.com/TrollVNC-1.6.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'Battman Battery Manager', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a2281624cc274.22979949.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 80, '1.0.3.2', '656.9 KB', NULL, 'Battman IPA: Advanced Battery Manager for iOS\n\nWant deeper control over your iPhone’s battery health? Battman IPA is an open-source battery manager that works on TrollStore-compatible and jailbroken devices, giving you pro-level diagnostics Apple doesn’t allow.\n\nUnlike iOS’s basic battery settings, Battman reveals detailed data like:', 'https://github.com/Torrekie/Battman/releases/download/v1.0.3.2/Battman.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'ImmortalizerTS', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a2281631a6bd9.12179449.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 90, '1.0', '84.8 KB', NULL, 'Keep your apps running indefinitely in the foreground, even when they’re pushed to the background — no jailbreak needed!\n\nImmortalizerTS is a TrollStore version of the popular Immortalizer tweak, designed to keep apps active and responsive at all times. It uses clever methods to work on iOS 15 and above without requiring jailbreak access.\n\nKey Features:', 'https://github.com/sergealagon/ImmortalizerTS/releases/download/Release/ImmortalizerTS.1.0b.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d7b812ff4.13772170.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'Reveil', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228163e1b759.81139184.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 100, '1.0', '', NULL, 'Reveil – Advanced System & Security Analysis for TrollStore (iOS 15 – 17.0)\n\nReveil is a powerful system monitoring and security analysis tool designed for TrollStore-compatible devices running iOS 15 to iOS 17.0. It brings back in-depth insights into your device’s performance, network activity, and system data, without needing a jailbreak.\n\nKey Features:', 'https://github.com/Lessica/Reveil/releases/download/v3.3.2-415/Reveil_3.3.2.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d7cb96746.33641032.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'SpeedGG', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228164afc682.39478378.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 110, '1.0', '1.1 MB', NULL, 'SpeedGG for iOS – Real-Time Internet Speed Widget (TrollStore Required)\n\nWant to see your iPhone’s internet speed live on your screen? SpeedGG is a simple and powerful widget built for TrollStore devices that shows your real-time download and upload speeds—right on your Home Screen. Whether you’re watching videos, downloading files, or just browsing, SpeedGG keeps you informed with clean, live stats.\n\nSpeedGG is a lightweight tool that adds a floating HUD (Heads-Up Display) to your iPhone, showing live internet speeds like “120KB/s ↓” and “80KB/s ↑”. It updates in real time, so you always know how your connection is performing.', 'https://github.com/qbap/ONEJailbreak/raw/refs/heads/main/SpeedGG_3.3_Eng.ipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'BatteryInfo', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228165844b05.78969296.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 120, '1.0', '338.8 KB', NULL, 'BatteryInfo IPA is a handy utility for checking and recording battery information on your iPhone or iPad. It provides detailed insights into your battery’s health, charge cycles, capacity, and real-time status, helping you monitor its performance over time.\n\nThis app is designed for TrollStore users, meaning you’ll need TrollStore installed on your device to use it. BatteryInfo supports iOS 14.0 – iOS 17.0, making it compatible with a wide range of devices.\n\n🔋 Key Features:', 'https://github.com/DevelopCubeLab/BatteryInfo/releases/download/1.2.2/com.developlab.batteryinfo_1.2.2.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d7e9c2908.37181076.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollWatcher', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228166574748.75669643.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 130, '1.0', '', NULL, 'Want a faster way to launch apps and control settings on your iPhone? TrollWatcher Lite is a lightweight utility for iOS 14 – iOS 17.0 that works perfectly with TrollStore. It lets you open apps, toggle features like Bluetooth, Dark Mode, and Location Services, and manage background apps — all from a fan-style menu right on your Home Screen. No jailbreak required!\n\nTrollWatcher Lite is a smart shortcut tool made for iPhones running TrollStore. Instead of constantly opening your Settings app, you can quickly toggle settings and open apps with a tap using a floating menu that pops out like a fan.\n\nIt’s small, smooth, and super useful for speeding up your daily tasks. Want to move the buttons or change how the menu looks? Just long-press the “+” icon to customize everything — no coding or deep setup needed.', 'https://mega.nz/file/u6IknJIL#tWEDnAMDvK6dKmwJyya1gUedwSM7XkTvoEAnPXHIPv8', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollCleanTool', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a2281672a03b1.22242827.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 140, '1.0', '1.8 MB', NULL, 'Free Up Space & Boost Performance: TrollCleanTool IPA for iOS 15 – 17.0.\n\nIs your iPhone running slow or cluttered with leftover jailbreak files? TrollCleanTool is here to help. It’s a lightweight, safe-to-use tool that cleans junk files, clears app caches, and frees up memory — all without harming your device. And yes, it works only when installed with TrollStore (no jailbreak required).\n\nTrollCleanTool is a simple utility for iOS 15 to iOS 17.0 that helps you clean your iPhone or iPad. Whether you’ve used jailbreak tools or just want to tidy up your system, this app clears out:', 'https://github.com/qbap/ONEJailbreak/raw/refs/heads/main/TrollCleanTool.ipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'ChargeLimiter', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228167eb83d9.59036147.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 150, '1.0', '2.4 MB', NULL, 'ChargeLimiter IPA – Extend iPhone Battery Life with Smart Charging Limits\n\nOptimizing how your iPhone charges can greatly extend battery health and prevent long-term wear. ChargeLimiter IPA is a free, open-source app that protects your battery by stopping overcharging. The best part? It now supports TrollStore, so you don’t need a jailbreak to use it.\n\nInspired by AlDente for macOS, ChargeLimiter is built to keep your iPhone battery healthy. It works on iOS 12 to iOS 17 and supports both jailbroken devices and TrollStore installations.', 'https://github.com/lich4/ChargeLimiter/releases/download/1.7/ChargeLimiter_1.7.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'ExtractApp', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228168c63fa1.15781069.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 160, '1.0', '127.4 KB', NULL, 'ExtractApp IPA – Easy App Extraction for iOS\n\nExtractApp, developed by DevelopCubeLab, is a powerful TrollStore-compatible tool that allows you to extract apps from your iPhone or iPad as IPA or TIPA files. Unlike other tools like DowngradeApp, ExtractApp does not decrypt the files, keeping them encrypted while making extraction simple.\n\nAfter installing, you can browse both your installed and system apps. The tool copies app files into a Payload folder, compresses them, and saves them as .ipa or .tipa files. You can also use a file manager like Filza to do this manually.', 'https://github.com/DevelopCubeLab/ExtractApp/releases/download/1.2/ExtractApp_1.2.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'TheBall', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228169bf0461.40193058.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 170, '1.0', '', NULL, 'The Ball is a simple and handy tweak for iPhones running iOS 14 to iOS 17.0. It works perfectly with TrollStore—no jailbreak needed!\n\nIt adds a small floating button to your home screen that you can move around. Just tap it to open your favorite apps like Safari, Messages, or anything else you choose. It’s a fast and easy way to access what you use most, and a great way to customize your device without risk.\n\n✅ Works with TrollStore✅ No jailbreak required✅ Easy to use and super customizable', 'https://ipa.cypwn.xyz/serve/get.php?md5=90787693eff99972f13f99c307f8af94', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d7f92a1d7.72540213.jpg"]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollRecorder', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816a916e11.05398795.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 180, '1.0', '', NULL, 'Record Calls Easily with TrollRecorder – No Jailbreak Needed!\n\nTrollRecorder is a reliable call recording app designed for TrollStore-supported devices, working smoothly on iOS 15.0 to 17.0. With its simple and user-friendly interface, recording important calls on your iPhone has never been easier!\n\nWhether you need to save business calls, personal conversations, or key details for future reference, TrollRecorder ensures you never miss a moment. Just install it through TrollStore and start recording with ease—no complicated setup or jailbreak required!', 'https://github.com/Lessica/TrollRecorder/releases/download/v3.5.5-3290/TRApp_3.5.5-3294.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'AppDump', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816b643919.21546783.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 190, '1.0', '4.4 MB', NULL, 'AppDump3 (previously AppDump2) is a simple yet powerful tool that lets you decrypt iOS apps and save them as IPA files—no jailbreak required! 📱💾 Whether you’re a developer looking to tweak apps or a user who wants to back up and share IPAs, AppDump makes the entire process quick and effortless.\n\nBuilt for TrollStore 2, AppDump3 works on iOS 15 through iOS 16 and may even support iOS 17 devices. The app takes full advantage of TrollStore’s system-level abilities to decrypt App Store apps right from your device, allowing you to export them as binaries or complete IPA packages.\n\nOnce installed through TrollStore, AppDump3 appears on your Home Screen. If developer mode is disabled, the app may fail to open—so make sure it’s turned on.', 'https://github.com/qbap/ONEJailbreak/raw/refs/heads/main/AppsDump3.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'EnableQUIC', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816c367170.80032342.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 200, '1.0', '327.7 KB', NULL, 'EnableQUIC is a TrollStore app that lets you activate QUIC (Quick UDP Internet Connections) on your device. This transport layer network protocol has been built into iOS starting with iOS 15+.\n\nDownload EnableQUIC IPA from your computer to install it using Altstore, Sideloadly, TrollStore, Scarlet, e-Sign, 3uTools, or MapleSign.\n\nv 1.1', 'https://github.com/DevelopCubeLab/EnableQUIC/releases/download/1.1/EnableQUIC_1.1.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d80c59b23.48345704.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'OTADisabler', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816d0b0ff8.78971012.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 210, '1.2.0', '215.2 KB', NULL, 'OTADisabler IPA by ichitaso lets you disable automatic iOS updates on iPhone and iPad running iOS 9 through the latest iOS 26+ versions.\n\nYou can easily install it using TrollStore or an OTA Update Blocker profile — no jailbreak required.\n\nOriginally, OTADisabler only worked on jailbroken devices, but newer versions now support non-jailbroken installation methods as well.', 'https://github.com/ichitaso/file/raw/main/tipa/OTADisabler_1.2.0.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'AnimationSpeed', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816dcc80b6.42705693.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 220, '1.0', '94.4 KB', NULL, 'AnimationSpeed lets you adjust animation speed across all apps on devices compatible with TrollStore. Normally, iOS doesn’t allow animation customization, but with this tool, you can fine-tune them to your preference.\n\n✅ Free to download for iOS 14 – 17.0✅ Easy installation via TrollStore IPA Installer✅ New updates include English support, a new icon, and an improved UI\n\nSpeed up your iOS experience with AnimationSpeed! 🚀', 'https://github.com/DevelopCubeLab/AnimationSpeed/releases/download/1.0.1/AnimationSpeed_1.0.1.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d81a877e5.09346540.jpg"]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollLEDs', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816e9bd4c5.70277512.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 230, '1.0', '81.4 KB', NULL, '🔦 TrollStore LED Manager for iOS!\n\nTake full control of your iPhone’s flashlight LEDs with TrollStore! Whether you want to tweak your device’s lighting or just experiment with different LED settings, this app has you covered. 📱✨\n\n✅ Manage Amber + White LED colors✅ Works on iOS 12 and newer✅ No jailbreak required!', 'https://github.com/PoomSmart/TrollLEDs/releases/download/1.9.0/TrollLEDs-unsandboxed.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d82cf5c84.13014874.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'Blossom', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a22816f6d7213.13364834.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 240, '1.0', '25 MB', NULL, 'Blossom is a simple yet powerful app for non-jailbroken devices on iOS 17.0, designed to replace your Lock Screen & Home Screen’s Live Photo with your video file.\n\nDownload Blossom IPA from your computer to install it using Altstore, Sideloadly, TrollStore, Scarlet, e-Sign, 3uTools, or MapleSign.\n\nv 1.1.1', 'https://github.com/inyourwalls/Blossom/releases/download/1.1.1/Blossom.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d8466c779.30304525.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'UiharuX Pro', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a2281703d91a2.84136596.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 250, '1.0', '3.2 MB', NULL, 'Download UiharuX Pro IPA – Customize iOS Without Jailbreak (iOS 14 – 17.0)\n\nUiharuX Pro Beta is an all-in-one iOS customization tweak that works perfectly with TrollStore — no jailbreak needed! Compatible with iOS 14 to iOS 17.0, it brings advanced features to your iPhone or iPad.\n\nTop Features:', 'https://github.com/straight-tamago/UiharuX/releases/download/2.0/com.straight-tamago.uiharux-pro-2.0.tipa', '[]'),
('trollstore', 'UI Speed', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228171127513.63104171.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 260, '1.0', '68.1 KB', NULL, 'UI Speed IPA is designed specifically for iPhone and iPad devices running iOS 14 through iOS 17.0. Exclusively compatible with TrollStore, this app speeds up animations in iOS, making your device feel noticeably faster and delivering a smoother, more responsive user experience.\n\n🔹 Key Features:\n\nGet UI Speed IPA now and take your iPhone or iPad to the next level!', 'https://t.co/ye0LC7UbmA', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d85b122f8.85526642.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'PureKFD', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228171d735b6.91088785.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 270, '1.0', '39.4 MB', NULL, 'PurePKG is a powerful package manager built for iOS 15 to 16.6.1 and iOS 18+. It’s designed for users who want to customize their devices with a modern, jailbreak-style experience, without needing a full jailbreak.\n\nDownload the PurePKG IPA to your computer and install it on your iPhone or iPad using tools like AltStore, Sideloadly, TrollStore, Scarlet, eSign, 3uTools, or MapleSign—no jailbreak required.\n\nv_5.3', 'https://github.com/Lrdsnow/PureKFD5/releases/download/5.3/purekfd.ipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d8738c813.41849156.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'Write Now Lite', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228172a736a4.63469816.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 280, '1.0', '2.4 MB', NULL, 'iOS 18 is set to bring new AI features that simplify task management, including a tool that can write or rewrite text based on its content. While these features won’t be available on older iOS versions, you can still try Write Now Lite. Originally designed for jailbreak devices, it can now be installed via TrollStore.\n\nWrite Now Lite is a demo app that lets you test the tweak without jailbreaking. The Lite version requires injecting apps using TrollFools, with insert_dylib and ChOma for smooth tweak injection. Instantly transform text while prioritizing privacy, supporting AI platforms like OpenAI, TogetherAI, OpenRouter, Groq, and NVIDIA NIM.\n\nDownload Write Now Lite IPA from your computer to install it using Altstore, Sideloadly, TrollStore, Scarlet, e-Sign, 3uTools, or MapleSign.', 'https://github.com/OwnGoalStudio/WriteNow/raw/main/Resources/LiteEdition/WriteNowLite_1.7.5.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d88355a33.24453269.jpg"]'),
('trollstore', 'TrollApps', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a2281737838f5.81668829.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 290, '1.0', '5.3 MB', NULL, 'TrollApps is a user-friendly tool that makes it easy to access apps compatible with the TrollStore installer on iOS 14 to 17. Created by haxi0 and now maintained by the Resonance Team, TrollApps offers a new interface and enhanced features.\n\nOnce installed, TrollApps integrates into your Home Screen like any other app. While it works with any IPA installer, using TrollStore or TrollStore 2 is recommended for the best experience. TrollApps comes preloaded with two repositories, giving you access to apps like Jaility, TrollBoard, Flappy Brid, Delta, and iTorrent. You can easily browse and search through the repositories to find and install apps compatible with TrollStore.\n\nTrollApps supports AltStore Sources and Repos, providing access to a wide range of apps and games. Adding new repositories is simple—just enter the URL, and you can access a variety of apps complete with descriptions, screenshots, and download links.', 'https://github.com/TheResonanceTeam/TrollApps/releases/download/2.3/org.resonance.store_2.3_082724.ipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d89b13798.05901383.png","assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d8b7e4863.67702386.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'SuperIcons', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228174491c42.97576035.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 300, '1.0', '2.2 MB', NULL, 'SuperIcons is a handy tool for customizing application icons on devices using TrollStore. It makes it easy to replace or restore icons for supported apps, giving you more control over your device’s look.\n\nDownload SuperIcons IPA from your computer to install it using Altstore, Sideloadly, TrollStore, Scarlet, e-Sign, 3uTools, or MapleSign.\n\nv2.1-4', 'https://github.com/huami1314/SuperIcons/releases/download/v2.1-4/SuperIcons.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d8e886f25.11719887.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'Batteried', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228175157c64.49817683.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 310, '1.0', '1.7 MB', NULL, 'Batteried for TrollStore – Add a GIF to Your Battery Icon!\n\nCreated by @Little_34306, Batteried is a simple yet fun app that lets you overlay a GIF on your battery icon on the Home Screen. It uses a smart HUD effect—inspired by the Helium app—to keep the animation perfectly in place.\n\n✨ Works on all devices – Notch, Dynamic Island, or Home button? No problem!✨ Supports iOS 15 – 16.6.1 & iOS 17.0✨ Customize your battery icon with a moving GIF', 'https://github.com/34306/batteried/releases/download/1.0/batteried_1.0.tipa', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d90535ab8.75084079.png"]'),
('trollstore', 'AirTroller', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228175d8d928.54304087.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 320, '1.0', '', NULL, 'AirTroller – AirDrop Flooder for iOS 14 to 15.7.1 (TrollStore Support)\n\nAirTroller is a fun AirDrop prank tool built for TrollStore-supported devices. It works by quickly sending and canceling AirDrop requests just as the recipient receives them—flooding their screen without sending actual files. It’s great for harmless fun with friends on iOS 14 to iOS 15.7.1.\n\nYes! AirTroller was initially set to be released as a $4.99 paid tweak due to the time and effort invested in its development. However, since iOS 16 introduced stronger AirDrop protections (like auto-decline), the tweak’s impact was reduced. It still works well on iOS 14 – 15.7.1, and if you find it useful, donations are always welcome!', 'https://apps.senumy.com/ipa-installer/airtroller/', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d94188496.10792759.jpg"]'),
('trollstore', 'AppStore+', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a229e93e05c18.64182228.jpg', '', '', 'TrollStore', 330, '1.0', '', NULL, 'AppStore++ IPA – Control App Versions on Your iPhone or iPad.\n\nAppStore++ gives you full control over your apps by letting you downgrade, upgrade, or block updates directly from the App Store. Whether you’re using a jailbroken or non-jailbroken device, AppStore++ helps you keep the app versions you like without being forced into updates.\n\nKey Features:', 'http://apps.senumy.com/ipa-installer/appstore+', '["assets/trollstore/screenshots/img_6a229d97307f78.73807163.jpg"]'),
