('trollstore', 'DowngradeApp', 'assets/trollstore/icons/img_6a228178ddb252.15497329.png', '', '', 'TrollStore', 350, '1.0', '', NULL, 'DowngradeApp – Manage, Upgrade, or Downgrade Apps on iOS with TrollStore\n\nDowngradeApp IPA by Netskao is a powerful utility designed for TrollStore and TrollStore 2 users. It gives you full control over your installed apps — letting you view app versions, manage installations, and even downgrade or upgrade apps directly from your iPhone or iPad.\n\nCompatible with iOS 14 to iOS 17, DowngradeApp provides a clean interface where you can easily browse all installed apps, see their version numbers and bundle identifiers, and generate download links to switch between available versions.', 'https://mega.nz/file/HyIkkQhL#oEJf_LY4x78cyC25GL3quZ3f9TCRx-n0NuUprzcQdho', '[]'),
